      <h1>Documentary Production in Switzerland: A Prime Location</h1>
      <p class="lead">Discover why Switzerland is a prime location for documentary production, from stunning landscapes to funding and multilingual crews.</p>
      <p class="post-meta"><span>Sofia Treviño</span> <span>·</span> <span>January 13, 2025</span> <span>·</span> <span>Updated March 24, 2025</span></p>
